    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >雪人进入人类世的旅程</h2><br>有一天，小雪人从一个漫长的梦中醒来，因为天气太热了。他需要你的帮助来找到热的原因。加入他的漫长旅程吧。并让他保持凉爽。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284860/extras/0c8d0b609457aa4ce3514b2e37024573.poster.avif?t=1737620518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284860/extras/0c8d0b609457aa4ce3514b2e37024573.webm?t=1737620518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284860/extras/0c8d0b609457aa4ce3514b2e37024573.mp4?t=1737620518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VR木偶平台游戏</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>类似木偶的控制方式<br></li><li>VRosty像木偶一样悬挂在你的手掌下<br></li><li>用操纵杆移动，按住A键，让他跟着你。<br></li><li>迅速向上移动控制器来跳跃<br></li><li>用扳机按钮投掷雪球，并通过倾斜你的手进行瞄准。<br></li><li>解决基于物理学和独特控制方法的难题<br></li><li>通过完成&gt;30个关卡来帮助Vrosty<br></li><li>收集&gt;100片雪花<br></li><li>保持凉爽<br></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284860/extras/1a551b1d610936cdef4d394465a14697.poster.avif?t=1737620518\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284860/extras/1a551b1d610936cdef4d394465a14697.webm?t=1737620518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284860/extras/1a551b1d610936cdef4d394465a14697.mp4?t=1737620518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
